# PROJECT_CONTEXT.md
# Project-Specific Context for the AI Development Framework
#
# HOW TO USE THIS FILE:
# 1. Copy this file to PROJECT_CONTEXT.md in the project root.
# 2. Fill in each section with your project's details.
# 3. Delete any section that does not apply.
# 4. Rules here override both CLAUDE.md and constitution.md.
#    More specific always wins.
#
# The Technical Director reads this file at the start of every session.
# Keep it accurate — outdated context is worse than no context.

