## Project-Specific Rules

> Rules here override CLAUDE.md and constitution.md. Add only rules that differ from the framework defaults.

- [e.g., "All database queries must use the ORM — raw SQL is not permitted except in explicitly annotated performance-critical methods."]
- [e.g., "The `payments` module requires two reviewers before merging — one must be the Backend Lead."]
- [e.g., "Security review is mandatory for ALL pull requests, not just those touching auth or PII."]
- [e.g., "Test coverage threshold is 95% for the `core` module, 80% for everything else."]

